snippet.title: Team Five - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
In "Team Five", you'll command a team of five animals with special abilities, competing against friends and global opponents in a race against the clock.
Collect valuable loot, obliterate the map, and GET THE HELL OUT before the world ends in just five minutes!
